&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and motivated individual to join the Cancer Services team for 30 hours a week to provide administrative support within the Two Week Wait Referrals Office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will possess excellent communication skills, will be efficient at organising and prioritising a busy workload and remain calm under pressure to achieve tight deadlines. The candidate will also have an understanding of patient and data confidentiality and the importance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In order to achieve these goals, the candidate will be required to work closely with clinical and administrative staff across the sites within the Trust and other Trusts within the region. This position is for 30 hours per week only.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants are advised that this vacancy may close early depending on the volume of applications received.&lt;/p&gt;
